quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  16,103,"We certainly know that they say, ‘It is only a human that instructs him.’ The language of him to whom they refer is non-Arabic, while this is a clear Arabic language"
  16,104,Indeed those who do not believe in the signs of Allah—Allah shall not guide them and there is a painful punishment for them
  16,105,"Only those fabricate lies who do not believe in the signs of Allah, and it is they who are the liars"
  16,106,"Excepting someone who is compelled [to recant his faith] while his heart is at rest in it, those who disbelieve in Allah after [affirming] their faith and open up their breasts to unfaith, Allah’s wrath shall be upon them and there is a great punishment for them"
  16,107,"That, because they preferred the life of the world to the Hereafter and that Allah does not guide the faithless lot"
  16,108,"They are the ones Allah has set a seal on their hearts, their hearing and their sight, and it is they who are the heedless"
  16,109,"Undoubtedly, they are the ones who will be the losers in the Hereafter"
  16,110,"Thereafter your Lord will indeed be forgiving and merciful to those who migrated after they were persecuted, waged jihad and remained steadfast"